scopia capital management  home firm overviewcontact us scopia capital management lp scopia is an institutional alternative asset management firm based in new york city with over  billion of assets under management founded in  by matt sirovich and jeremy mindich scopia employs a fundamentalsbased valuedriven investment approach across four strategies a longshort equity strategy managed with the discipline of market neutrality a longshort equity strategy managed with net long exposure a longonly equity strategy and a longshort health care focused strategy scopia has been an sec registered investment adviser since    scopia capital management lp all rights reserved scopia with the circle logo scopia capital and scopia are trademarks of scopia registered in the us patent and trademark office scopia capital management lp private company information  bloomberg july    am et capital markets company overview of scopia capital management lp snapshot people company overview scopia capital management lp is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor it provides its services to pooled investment vehicles including the hedge funds the long only fund and scip which are intended for institutional investors and other sophisticated investors the firm manages separate clientfocused equity portfolios it primarily invests in value stocks of companies the firm employs fundamental analysis to create its portfolios it employs longshort strategy to make its investments the firm was formerly known as scopia capital management llc scopia capital management lp was founded in  and is based in new york new york  west th streetrd floornew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwscopiacapitalcom key executives for scopia capital management lp mr jeremy hendrik mindich president founding partner managing partner portfolio manager and director mr matthew ivan sirovich founding partner age  mr aaron william morse partner and chief operating officer mr jerome j lande head of specialsituation invest